DESIGN ATM

1. Login to account using PIN.
2. Deposit money into bank account(after logged in)
3. Withdraw money from bank account(after logged in)
4. Check bank balance (after logged in)
5. While withdrawal -> user mention total amount and ATM will dispense denomination and remove from bank balance
6. While deposit -> User will push denomination and ATM will accept and add to bank balance
7. ATM Has Money(fixed) and Bank account details


Entities

1. Denomination - 100,200,500
2. Money - map of <denomination,integer> and has total amount
3. Bank account - userid, pinid, money
4. ATM Machine - has Money and list of bank account

Services
1. Different state of ATM - idle,loggedin,dispense,accepting money
2.Idle state -> Accepts log in
3. Loggedin state -> Accepts deposit request, withdrawal request and bank balance request. Fulfills bank balance request only
4.Dispense state -> Sending money to user, removing from bank account and ATM and returns to idle
5.Accepting state -> Takes money from user , adding to bankaccount and ATM and returns to idle